item.description:
@thisisdanbell Part 1 Here is a story for you. https://t.co/VYYiRqyEeo Part 2 Last Saturday night or the Saturday before, during the ride-along, you drove past a place where you worked & the boss got shot and died ... Is that the restaurant they were going to try to reopen?
@thisisdanbell I sent you the link to the story about 2.5 years ago. What was the name of that restaurant? I'd like to see you do a Doc on it.
